--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 512a72de08c75cf4e8a8424f7b75a271, type: 3}
  m_Name: D2T15_AdvisorTalkAfterIndian
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npc: 0
  sequence:
  - dialogueText: You actually took the crates? You've got more nerve than I thought.
      Or less sense.
    buttonText: Needed the coin
  - dialogueText: Bold move. But the Boss is a shark. If he catches a scent, you're
      dead before you hit the water.
    buttonText: What now?
  - dialogueText: Play it cool. Stick to the script. And don't risk your neck again
      unless the prize is truly valuable
    buttonText: Understood
  - dialogueText: Since your shift is over, why won't you head back to those chairs
      on the beach?
    buttonText: Nothing there
  - dialogueText: Just because they were empty yesterday doesn't mean they're empty
      tonight. This island has a short memory
    buttonText: I'll check
  - dialogueText: Wait... look at the counter. Why is he waving at you like that
      again?
    buttonText: Not again
  - dialogueText: He's persistent tonight. Go see what he wants. Keep your head straight
      until the pressure drops.
    buttonText: I'm going
